window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An exclusive prequel novella to the <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author's award-winning thriller series.</p> <p>FBI Special Agent Irene Rivers is horrified to learn that because of mistakes made by agents under her command, a murderer and child molester will walk free. But now her worst nightmare has come true: The monster has abducted Irene's own daughters. With nowhere else to turn, she reaches out to an elite Special Forces operator named Jonathan Grave.</p> <p>While Rivers has always observed the letter of the law, Grave cares more about results than procedures. Together, they will face a new breed of evil-and pursue a new kind of justice.</p>"; 
